CommentBody: In the meeting, permissions were assigned to Windows host and Proxy server as per documentation. Required ports are open. Deleted certificates as per KB (https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000WSvKAM.html). NEA version is 11.6.0.80 and Proxy version is 11.6.0.28. We have asked customer to update to latest version of NEA so that we can rule out the proxy compatibility issue.
